l; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">쇠고기는</font></font></em><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;&nbsp;간단하게 시작됩니다.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">지역 가전제품 매장에서 무례한 출납원의 정면 끝에 자신을 발견한 Danny(Steven Yeun)는 차를 타고 주차 공간에서 후퇴하기 시작합니다.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">불행히도 그는 바로 그 순간 그의 뒤에서 운전하고 있는 흰색 SUV를 보지 못합니다. 그의 운전사 Amy(Ali Wong)는 Danny의 트럭이 그녀에게 거의 후진하기 직전에 경적을 울립니다.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">잠시 후 Amy는 창문을 내리고 Danny를 뒤집어 비이성적으로 그녀를 주차장에서 쫓아 내도록 유도합니다.</font></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding:0px; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:NotoSans, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"background-color:#18181b\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">두 사람은 Amy의 교외 지역에서 위험한 자동차 추격전을 벌입니다.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">그러나 Amy가 승리를 거두며 그들의 관계가 끝나는 것처럼 보이지만 Amy와 Danny는 서로에 대한 적개심을 그렇게 쉽게 내버려 두지 않습니다.&nbsp;</font><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">Lee가 저술하고 Hikari 도쿄 부사장이</font></em><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;감독을 맡은&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></font><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">Beef</font></font></em><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;의 뛰어난 첫 번째 에피소드가 끝나야 할 때&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;Danny는 성공적으로 Amy를 추적하고 길에서 그녀의 정신병적인 무례함에 대해 보복했습니다.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">이에 대한 응답으로 Amy는 Danny를 추적하고 두 사람은 천천히 그러나 확실하게 Amy의 민감하지만 감정적으로 조종하는 남편 George(Joseph Lee)와 Danny의 남동생을 포함하여 가장 가까운 가족과 사랑하는 사람들을 모두 포함하도록 성장하는 불화를 시작합니다. 폴(영 마지노).</font></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding:0px; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:NotoSans, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"background-color:#18181b\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">10개의 에피소드에서&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></font><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">Beef는</font></font></em><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;&nbsp;젠더 정치, 세대적 트라우마, 다양한 경제 계층 구성원 사이에 존재할 수 있는 괴로움에 대한 현대적 생각을 다룹니다.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">자수성가한 부자 사업가 에이미는 대니의 재정적 불안정과 저소득을 반복적으로 이용하여 그를 공개적으로 부끄럽게 만들려고 합니다.&nbsp;</font></font><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">Beef는</font></font></em><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;&nbsp;캐릭터의 삶의 정치적, 경제적 측면을 다루는 것을 부끄러워하지 않지만 결코 그들에게 너무 집중하여 쇼의 요점이 되지 않습니다&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">대신, 이 시리즈는 다른 사람들을 자신의 분노와 좌절을 위한 그릇으로 사용하는 것이 그 어느 때보다 쉬워진 21세기의 삶의 초상화를 더욱 구체화하기 위해 그것들을 사용합니다.</font></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<figure aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3315842\" id=\"attachment_3315842\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; display:block; padding:0px; color:#ffffff; font-family:NotoSans, sans-serif; font-size:16px; font-style:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-weight:400; text-align:left; white-space:normal; background-color:#18181b; text-decoration-thickness:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial\">\r\n<p style=\"padding:0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><img alt=\"Ali Wong과 Joseph Lee는 Beef에서 함께 웃고 있습니다.\" data-dt-lazy-src=\"https://www.digitaltrends.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Ali-Wong-and-Joseph-Lee-smile-together-in-BEEF.jpg?fit=720%2C480&amp;p=1\" decoding=\"async\" onerror=\"dti_load_error(this)\" src=\"https://www.digitaltrends.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Ali-Wong-and-Joseph-Lee-smile-together-in-BEEF.jpg?fit=720%2C480&amp;p=1\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:middle; border:0px; max-width:100%\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3315842\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; display:block\">\r\n<p style=\"padding:0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">넷플릭스</font></font></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding:0px; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:NotoSans, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"background-color:#18181b\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">이 시리즈는 어느 시점에서도 Danny나 Amy가 그들의 행동에 대해 책임을 지지 않도록 합니다.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">초기에&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></font><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">Beef</font></font></em><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;에서는 &nbsp;등장인물들이 직면하고 싶지 않은 자신의 삶의 측면에 대한 분노와 슬픔을 몰아내기 위해 불화를 사용하고 있음이 분명해졌습니다.&nbsp;</font></font><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">그러나 Amy와 Danny의 비합리적인 행동 뒤에 숨겨진 이유를 탐구하려는 Beef</font></font></em><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;의 관심은 너무 멀리 확장되지 않습니다.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">쇼는 가늘게 뜨인 눈으로 자신의 세대 적 트라우마에 대한 감정적 단점을 비난하려는 에이미의 시도까지 충족합니다.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">시즌 후반의 멋진 트위스트에서&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></font><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">Beef는</font></font></em><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;&nbsp;또한 Danny가 자신의 삶의 문제에 대해 항상 다른 사람을 비난할 수는 없다는 사실을 직시하도록 강요합니다.</font></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding:0px; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:NotoSans, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"background-color:#18181b\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">그들의 경쟁이 점점 더 위험해질수록 Danny와 Amy는 여러 면에서 소울메이트라는 사실이 더욱 분명해집니다.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">이성진은 두 인물의 무모한 행동과 자비의 순간을 통해 한 사람과의 정서적 궁합이 어떻게 최고의 친구이자 최악의 적이 될 수 있는지를 드러낸다.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">Wong과 Yeun은 놀라운 수준의 분노와 절망으로 캐릭터의 정서적 가시성을 탐구합니다.&nbsp;</font></font><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">Beef는</font></font></em><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;&nbsp;두 배우에게 그들의 경력 중 최고의 연기를 선보일 수 있는 기회를 제공합니다.&nbsp;</font><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">대니가 쇠고기</font></em><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;중 하나에서 갑작스런 고장을 경험하는 Yeun의 경우 특히 그렇습니다.&nbsp;</font></font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">배우가 그 어느 때보 다 화면에서 적나라하게 노출되어야하는 초기 에피소드.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">비극과 유머의 경계를 잘 넘나드는 이 장면은 깨지지 않는 긴 테이크를 통해 예은이 채굴하는 감정의 깊이로 인해 거대해집니다.</font></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding:0px; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:NotoSans, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"background-color:#18181b\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">쇼의 앙상블 캐스트를 마무리하면서 Young Mazino는 앞으로 몇 달 동안 배우가 많은 주목을 받을 Paul로 획기적인 공연을 선보입니다.&nbsp;</font></font><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">Beef</font></font></em><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;의 많은&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">캐릭터와 마찬가지로 Paul은 자신의 외향적 페르소나(암호화 형제)를 사용하여 다른 연기자의 손에서 해미처럼 보일 수 있는 근본적인 불안과 연결에 대한 절박한 갈망을 숨깁니다.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">그러나 Mazino는 Paul 안에 너무 많은 모순된 감정과 충동이 존재할 수 있다는 생각을 사게 만듭니다.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">다른 곳에서는 David Choe, Ashley Park, Justin H. Min이 Amy와 Danny의 삶을 조연으로 하는 세 명의 인물로 비슷하게 잘 보정된 연기를 보여줍니다.</font></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<figure aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3315843\" id=\"attachment_3315843\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; display:block; padding:0px; color:#ffffff; font-family:NotoSans, sans-serif; font-size:16px; font-style:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-weight:400; text-align:left; white-space:normal; background-color:#18181b; text-decoration-thickness:initial; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial\">\r\n<p style=\"padding:0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><img alt=\"Bobby, Michael, Danny, Paul은 Beef에서 함께 농구 코트에 서 있습니다.\" data-dt-lazy-src=\"https://www.digitaltrends.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Bobby-Michael-Danny-and-Paul-stand-on-basketball-court-together-in-BEEF.jpg?fit=720%2C480&amp;p=1\" decoding=\"async\" onerror=\"dti_load_error(this)\" src=\"https://www.digitaltrends.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Bobby-Michael-Danny-and-Paul-stand-on-basketball-court-together-in-BEEF.jpg?fit=720%2C480&amp;p=1\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:middle; border:0px; max-width:100%\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3315843\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; display:block\">\r\n<p style=\"padding:0px\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">앤드류 쿠퍼/넷플릭스</font></font></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding:0px; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:NotoSans, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"background-color:#18181b\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">시각적으로&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></font><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">Beef는</font></font></em><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;&nbsp;지난 몇 년 동안 가장 뛰어난 쇼 중 하나입니다.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">이성진, 히카리,&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></font><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">페이퍼 타운스의</font></font></em><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;&nbsp;제이크 슈라이어 감독이 연출을 분담했고, 후자가 첫 10개 에피소드 중 6개 에피소드를 지휘했다.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">함께 그들은 일관되게 놀랍고 햇빛에 흠뻑 젖은 영화 촬영법을 특징으로 할 뿐만 아니라 깨지지 않고 반드시 화려한 카메라 촬영의 가치를 알고 있는 쇼를 제공했습니다.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;항상 눈물이 날 것 같은 눈을 통해 그들의 감정이 펼쳐지면서 카메라가 단순히 Wong과 Yeun의 얼굴에 놓이는&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></font><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">Beef</font></font></em><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;전체에 여러 사례가 있습니다&nbsp; .&nbsp;</font></font><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">소고기</font></font></em><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;는 시청자가 이야기의 어려운 감정에 앉도록 강요하는 것을 두려워하지 않으며 시각적 스타일은 내러티브 인내심을 반영합니다.</font></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding:0px; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:NotoSans, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"background-color:#18181b\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; verti