-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">전반적으로&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></font><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">Simulant는&nbsp;</font></font></em><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">&nbsp;반드시 나쁜 영화는 아니지만 어떤 식으로든 눈에 띄거나 담론에 아무것도 추가하지 못하는 단조로운 영화일 뿐입니다.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\">그럼에도 불구하고 장르 팬들은 여기서 충분히 찾을 수 있을 것이다.</font></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding:0px; text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:NotoSans, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"background-color:#18181b\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><b style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-weight:bolder\"><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; font-style:normal\"><font style=\"box-sizing:border-box; word-break:break-all; overflow-wrap:break-word; vertical-align:inherit\